Get USPORTS wrestling team rankings

Source: R/wrestling_team_rankings.R
wrestling_team_rankings.Rd

Get USPORTS wrestling team rankings

Usage

wrestling_team_rankings(gender)

Arguments

gender

Gender of athletes "m" or "w"

Value

A data frame.

Examples

wrestling_team_rankings("m")
